name: com.android.dialer.precall.externalreceiver.LaunchPreCallActivity
description: Activity that forwards to PreCall#start(Context, CallIntentBuilder) so the pre-call flow can be initiated by external apps. This activity is exported but can only be started by apps with android.Manifest.permission#CALL_PHONE. Keyguard will be triggered if phone is locked. @see CallIntentBuilder
